budget is working against you.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1011\" data-end=\"1318\">Speed is non-negotiable. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.thinkwithgoogle.com\/intl\/en-emea\/marketing-strategies\/app-and-mobile\/mobile-page-speed-data\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google\u2019s research<\/a> shows that every additional second of mobile load time can reduce conversions by up to 20%. Separate studies have shown that even a 0.1-second improvement can lift conversions by 8%+ in retail contexts. In short, slow pages tax your ROI; faster pages compound it.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1320\" data-end=\"1637\">Copy clarity matters. Unbounce\u2019s multi-year analysis of 57M+ conversions found that difficult, complex copy correlates with meaningfully lower conversion performance. Simpler, benefit-led language consistently converts better, and top-quartile pages in many categories post double-digit conversion rates as a result.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1639\" data-end=\"2072\">Testing changes outcomes. You do not need a redesign to move the needle. Structured A\/B tests on headlines, forms, and CTAs routinely produce material uplifts when they reach significance. In one large dataset, experiments that did hit significance delivered an average lift of 61% versus control. You will not get that every time, but the compounding effect of iterative wins is what separates average accounts from efficient ones.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2074\" data-end=\"2119\">What this means for your budgets in Kenya<\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2121\" data-end=\"2780\">\n<li data-start=\"2121\" data-end=\"2340\">\n<p data-start=\"2123\" data-end=\"2340\"><strong data-start=\"2123\" data-end=\"2134\">Problem<\/strong>: You are paying to acquire traffic that arrives primarily on mobile. Slow loads, generic messaging, and long forms kill intent and inflate cost per acquisition. Mobile-heavy markets magnify the penalty.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2341\" data-end=\"2532\">\n<p data-start=\"2343\" data-end=\"2532\"><strong data-start=\"2343\" data-end=\"2355\">Solution<\/strong>: Purpose-built, campaign-specific pages that are fast on mobile, message-matched to the ad, clear in copy, short in forms, and instrumented for measurement and rapid testing.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2533\" data-end=\"2780\">\n<p data-start=\"2535\" data-end=\"2780\"><strong data-start=\"2535\" data-end=\"2546\">Benefit<\/strong>: More leads or sales from the same spend, lower CPA, and better return on ad spend because you are converting more of the clicks you already bought. Benchmarks indicate there is headroom above the 6\u20137% \u201caverage\u201d if you execute well.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2782\" data-end=\"3073\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">If you are currently sending paid traffic to a homepage, a slow product page, or a one-size-fits-all template, you are almost certainly leaving revenue on the table. Start by fixing the conversion leaks, then scale your spend once your cost per lead or sale stabilises at a profitable level.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"49\">Signs Your Landing Pages Are Costing You Sales<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"51\" data-end=\"323\">If you are running ads but conversions are not improving, the problem often lies with the landing page. Paid campaigns can bring thousands of visitors, but if the page does not guide them clearly towards action, those clicks are wasted. Here are the most common red flags:<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"325\" data-end=\"357\">High bounce rates from ads<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"358\" data-end=\"497\">If 70\u201380% of people leave within seconds of landing, it signals a mismatch between your ad promise and the page content, or poor usability.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"499\" data-end=\"548\">Lots of traffic, but few enquiries or sales<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"549\" data-end=\"695\">When you see clicks and impressions going up but leads or purchases stay flat, your landing page is not persuading visitors to take the next step.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"697\" data-end=\"732\">Long forms that users abandon<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"733\" data-end=\"884\">In Kenya, where mobile usage dominates, lengthy or complicated forms are a conversion killer. Shorter, focused forms increase the chance of completion.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"886\" data-end=\"930\">Slow load speeds, especially on mobile<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"1111\">A one-second delay can mean a 20% drop in conversions. Many Kenyan users browse with mid-range devices and average internet speeds, so fast-loading, lightweight pages are critical.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1113\" data-end=\"1158\">Generic pages not tailored to campaigns<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1159\" data-end=\"1323\">Sending traffic from different ads to the same generic page ignores user intent. Campaign-specific pages that speak directly to the ad\u2019s promise convert far better.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1325\" data-end=\"1369\">Weak or unclear calls-to-action (CTAs)<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1523\">A vague \u201cLearn more\u201d button is less effective than a direct, benefit-driven CTA like \u201cGet your free consultation today\u201d or \u201cShop the new collection now.\u201d<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1370\" data-end=\"1523\">If you recognise any of these issues on your current landing pages, you are likely paying for clicks that never turn into revenue. Optimisation is not optional\u2014it is the only way to improve cost per lead or sale and protect your marketing spend.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"54\">What Our Landing Page Optimisation Services Include<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"56\" data-end=\"336\">A successful landing page is more than a pretty design. It is the product of structured analysis, smart copy, technical performance, and ongoing testing. Our landing page optimisation services in Kenya cover every element required to turn traffic into measurable leads or sales.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"338\" data-end=\"363\">Landing Page Audits<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"364\" data-end=\"448\">We start by assessing your current landing pages to find the leaks. This includes:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"449\" data-end=\"642\">\n<li data-start=\"449\" data-end=\"512\">\n<p data-start=\"451\" data-end=\"512\">Reviewing user experience, design flow, and content clarity<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"513\" data-end=\"585\">\n<p data-start=\"515\" data-end=\"585\">Using heatmaps and session recordings to see where visitors drop off<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"586\" data-end=\"642\">\n<p data-start=\"588\" data-end=\"642\">Analysing funnel performance to identify bottlenecks<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"644\" data-end=\"680\">Conversion-Focused Copywriting<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"681\" data-end=\"712\">Words drive action. We craft:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"713\" data-end=\"917\">\n<li data-start=\"713\" data-end=\"774\">\n<p data-start=\"715\" data-end=\"774\">Headlines that capture attention and echo your ad message<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"775\" data-end=\"848\">\n<p data-start=\"777\" data-end=\"848\">Body copy that highlights benefits and addresses pain points directly<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"849\" data-end=\"917\">\n<p data-start=\"851\" data-end=\"917\">Calls-to-action (CTAs) that are specific, urgent, and persuasive<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"919\" data-end=\"953\">Design &amp; Layout Improvements<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"954\" data-end=\"1027\">The structure of a page can make or break conversions. We optimise for:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1299\">\n<li data-start=\"1028\" data-end=\"1103\">\n<p data-start=\"1030\" data-end=\"1103\">Mobile-first usability (critical in Kenya where most traffic is mobile)<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1104\" data-end=\"1159\">\n<