ion<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"1932\" data-end=\"1967\">A\/B Testing &amp; Experimentation<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1968\" data-end=\"2007\">We test systematically, not randomly:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2008\" data-end=\"2185\">\n<li data-start=\"2008\" data-end=\"2057\">\n<p data-start=\"2010\" data-end=\"2057\">Running headline, CTA, and layout experiments<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2058\" data-end=\"2114\">\n<p data-start=\"2060\" data-end=\"2114\">Using multivariate testing on high-traffic campaigns<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2115\" data-end=\"2185\">\n<p data-start=\"2117\" data-end=\"2185\">Applying a continuous test\u2013learn\u2013implement cycle to keep improving<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2187\" data-end=\"2219\">Analytics &amp; Tracking Setup<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2220\" data-end=\"2276\">Without data, optimisation is guesswork. We implement:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"2277\" data-end=\"2451\">\n<li data-start=\"2277\" data-end=\"2322\">\n<p data-start=\"2279\" data-end=\"2322\">Google Analytics 4 and Google Tag Manager<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2323\" data-end=\"2386\">\n<p data-start=\"2325\" data-end=\"2386\">Conversion tracking for clicks, forms, calls, and purchases<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2387\" data-end=\"2451\">\n<p data-start=\"2389\" data-end=\"2451\">Custom dashboards with the KPIs that matter to your business<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Our landing page optimisation services in Kenya include detailed audits to identify leaks, covering the full spectrum of Conversion Rate Optimisation (CRO). We identify issues, fix them, test alternatives, and prove what works. This ensures your ad spend delivers measurable returns rather than wasted traffic.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"39\">Who Needs Landing Page Optimisation?<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"41\" data-end=\"332\">Landing page optimisation is not just for big brands with huge ad budgets. Any organisation investing in digital campaigns but struggling to see proportional returns will benefit from conversion rate optimisation (CRO). In Kenya, several groups stand out as the ones who can gain the most.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"334\" data-end=\"372\">Businesses running PPC campaigns<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"373\" data-end=\"592\">If you are investing in Google Ads, Facebook Ads, or LinkedIn Ads, every click you pay for needs to count. Sending traffic to a poorly optimised page increases your cost per lead and makes scaling campaigns difficult.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"594\" data-end=\"617\">E-commerce stores<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"618\" data-end=\"799\">Product-specific landing pages are the difference between browsing and buying. Optimised pages highlight trust signals, reduce friction at checkout, and increase cart completions.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"801\" data-end=\"868\">NGOs and institutions running awareness or donation campaigns<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"869\" data-end=\"1062\">When the goal is donations, sign-ups, or awareness, a cluttered or confusing landing page can undermine the campaign. Optimisation ensures your message is clear, credible, and easy to act on.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1064\" data-end=\"1109\">SaaS companies offering trials or demos<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1110\" data-end=\"1284\">For software providers, trials and demos are key entry points. Streamlined forms, strong value propositions, and frictionless pages can significantly improve sign-up rates.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1286\" data-end=\"1307\">Event marketers<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1308\" data-end=\"1480\">Whether it\u2019s a corporate summit, product launch, or educational training, a well-optimised registration page ensures higher attendance rates and fewer abandoned sign-ups.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1308\" data-end=\"1480\">If you are spending money to drive people to your website, whether through ads, email, or social media, you need high-converting landing pages to make that spend worthwhile.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"45\">Our Process for Optimising Landing Pages<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"47\" data-end=\"274\">Conversion Rate Optimisation (CRO) works best when it is structured, data-driven, and iterative. At Aminifu Digital Agency, we use a clear framework to ensure every change we recommend is backed by evidence and tested for impact.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"276\" data-end=\"334\">Step 1: Audit Current Performance and Identify Leaks<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"335\" data-end=\"580\">We begin by analysing your landing page performance data. This includes bounce rates, time on page, funnel drop-offs, and conversion paths. We also review page design, copy, speed, and mobile usability to identify where visitors lose interest.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"582\" data-end=\"645\">Step 2: Research User Behaviour and Competitor Benchmarks<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"886\">We use tools such as heatmaps, scroll tracking, and session replays to see exactly how users interact with your page. At the same time, we study competitors in Kenya and globally to benchmark performance and identify gaps you can exploit.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"888\" data-end=\"930\">Step 3: Build Hypotheses for Testing<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"931\" data-end=\"1008\">Instead of random changes, we create specific test hypotheses. For example:<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1170\">\n<li data-start=\"1009\" data-end=\"1084\">\n<p data-start=\"1011\" data-end=\"1084\">\u201cReducing the lead form to three fields will increase completion rate.\u201d<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1085\" data-end=\"1170\">\n<p data-start=\"1087\" data-end=\"1170\">\u201cChanging the CTA from \u2018Learn More\u2019 to \u2018Get My Free Audit\u2019 will increase clicks.\u201d<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1172\" data-end=\"1258\">Each hypothesis is prioritised based on potential impact and ease of implementation.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1260\" data-end=\"1307\">Step 4: Design and Deploy Test Variations<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1308\" data-end=\"1525\">Our design and development team creates variations of your landing page. These could include new layouts, headlines, CTAs, or form structures. We then run controlled A\/B or multivariate tests to compare performance.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1527\" data-end=\"1579\">Step 5: Measure, Refine, and Scale the Winners<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1839\">Once tests reach statistical significance, we adopt the winning variation. Over time, these small but consistent improvements compound into significant gains in lead generation or sales. We also build dashboards so you can see ROI improvements in real time.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1839\">Our process ensures we don\u2019t guess. Every optimisation is deliberate, measurable, and designed to improve your cost per acquisition and overall return on investment.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=&#8221;&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"51\">Why Choose Aminifu Digital Agency for CRO in Kenya<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"53\" data-end=\"330\">Optimising landing pages is not about guesswork; it is about applying proven frameworks backed by data. Many agencies can design pages, but very few in Kenya combine deep advertising experience with rigorous conversion optimisation. Here is why Aminifu Digital Agency stands out.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"332\" data-end=\"366\">Data-Driven, Not Assumptions<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"540\">Every recommendation we make is supported by analytics, A\/B test data, and user behaviour insights. This ensures changes are not based on opinion but on measurable impact.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"542\" data-end=\"586\">10+ Years of Experience in PPC and CRO<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"587\" data-end=\"838\">We have managed c