cific landing pages, we will improve them directly. If not, we create standalone landing pages tailored to your campaigns, hosted either within your site or on a dedicated subdomain.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"668\" data-end=\"720\">Q3: Do you provide design and development too?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"721\" data-end=\"950\">Yes. Our team includes designers, developers, and CRO specialists. This means we handle everything from copywriting and layout design to technical speed fixes and analytics tracking\u2014so you don\u2019t have to juggle multiple vendors.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"952\" data-end=\"1004\">Q4: What\u2019s the difference between CRO and SEO?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1005\" data-end=\"1289\">Conversion Rate Optimisation (CRO) focuses on improving the percentage of visitors who take action once they arrive on your page. Search Engine Optimisation (SEO) focuses on attracting more organic visitors to your site. They work best together: SEO brings traffic, CRO converts it.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1291\" data-end=\"1352\">Q5: Do I need separate landing pages for each campaign?<\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1353\" data-end=\"1583\">Yes. A single generic landing page rarely works across multiple campaigns. Tailoring landing pages to each ad group or audience ensures your message is highly relevant, which improves both click-through rate and conversion rate.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row full_width=&#8221;stretch_row&#8221; bg_type=&#8221;bg_color&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1717845133697{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}&#8221; bg_color_value=&#8221;#f4f4f4&#8243; el_id=&#8221;!\/contact&#8221;][vc_column]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-9407695ec19e5fc8f\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-9407695ec19e5fc8f uvc-4030  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"line_with_icon\" data-hline_width=\"100\" data-hicon_type=\"selector\" data-hborder_style=\"solid\" data-hborder_height=\"5\" data-hb